(43, 3, 36, 45, 1, 17, 18, 'the wrath of God abideth on him', 'Connection of Faith and Wrath', 'Both passages emphasize the consequences of belief and disbelief. John 3:36 speaks of the wrath of God abiding on those who do not believe in the Son, while Romans 1:18 reveals God''s wrath against unrighteousness, linking faith to the avoidance of divine wrath.', 'theme', 0.419, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
